Package: smFishPlateDesigner
Type: Package
Title: Plate Design and Layout for High-Throughput smFish
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Cédric HASSEN-KHODJA
Maintainer: Cédric HASSEN-KHODJA <cedric.hassen-khodja@mri.cnrs.fr>
Description: This package provides tools for designing and arranging plate layouts 
    for high-throughput single-molecule fluorescence in situ hybridization (HT-smFish) 
    experiments. It includes functions for processing raw data, organizing plate layouts, 
    and generating visual representations of the experimental setups.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
